      "review_summary": "Adds an opt-in `${VAR:json}` modifier to config env substitution and write-back preservation, with tests for array/object coercion and round-tripping.\n\nPR surface: Source +110, Tests +122. Total +232 across 4 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. by source inspection: current main always returns strings for string env substitutions, so `${VAR}` cannot materialize arrays/objects before schema validation. I did not run a live repro because this review was read-only.",
